WHO WE ARE
RORTOS
is an Italian company focused on flight simulators development for mobile.
It was
founded on 2012
and today is a major player on mobile market.
We offer a wide range of
simulation products
: civil, military, fighting, naval historians and helicopters.
Our products have reached
200 million downloads.
We develop and distribute software across all major platforms:
IOS, Android, Steam, Xbox One and PS4.
